* {{ill|Haniimasahime Shrine|ja|波爾移麻比禰神社}} (*Tokushima Prefecture*, Mima City) - {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社}}<ref name="JapaneseGods-Haniyasu"/>  
* {{ill|Maoka Shinden Shrine|ja|馬岡新田神社}} (*Tokushima Prefecture*, Miyoshi City) - {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社}}<ref name="JapaneseGods-Haniyasu"/>  
* {{ill|Haniro Shrine|ja|波爾布神社}} (*Shiga Prefecture*, Takashima City) - {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社}}<ref name="JapaneseGods-Haniyasu"/>  
