* {{ill|Maoka Shinden Shrine|ja|馬岡新田神社}} (*Tokushima Prefecture*, Miyoshi City)  
* {{ill|Haruna Shrine (Fujimi)|ja|榛名神社 (富士見市)}} (*Saitama Prefecture*, Fujimi City)  
