===Haniudanokami Shrine (ハニウダノカミ)===
* {{ill|Habuta Shrine|ja|土生田神社}} (*Niigata Prefecture*, Tagami Town) – Haniudanokami is regarded as another form of Haniyasu<ref name="JapaneseGods-Haniuda"/>.  
